Devalot 0.2
===========
This is primarily a feature release with a sprinkling of bug fixes.  This is an
alpha release intended for developers and extreme users only.

Visible:
* Search option.
* Ticket Timeline. (thanks to Sam Lown)
* Tweaks to default CSS style and layout.

Under the hood:
* Integrated search with Ferret.
* Rails 2.0.2
* Numerous little fixes.
* Removed relation to filtered_texts table in:
  - pages
  - projects

Devalot 0.1
===========
Initial alpha release.
